UPDATE companies SET agent_ids_notes = 'Notes: Surfacing Polytrade which is currently raising $5-6 M seed round. Team comes highly referenced from key crypto angels, have just launched their protocol and are now nearing the first $1M financing activity mark. There is high momentum to this round with Falcon, Sequoia India, Coinbase ventures, Draper Dragon, Hashed, Saison, already in advanced stages + early stage web3 funds already putting out TSs. We are excited because 1. A key thesis area in crypto for us is Defi-TradFi bridging 1. A complete team which has already shipped the protocol and cold started liquidity + financing cycle 1. Founder has great depth and experience in the underlying finance business (invoice discounting). We’d be looking out for - Execution risks : eg: currently routing fiat via DBS bank at SGP which could be a risk if DBS decides to not accept crypto as source of funds? what can be done to mitigate?) - Regulatory risks : KYC requirements, AML concerns etc - Accrual of value to equity and tokens cap tables and tokenomics + role of community in growth (investor GTM, future protocol growth) - Growth mindset and coachability of founder We are completing BRCs, expert conversations and lining up a founder convo with fin-tech team (Anish, AK) this week before bringing this to a meeting with you early next week. **About** [Polytrade](https://polytrade.finance/) is a trade finance co bridging DeFi (decentralised finance) and TradFI (traditional finance) using smart contracts and tokenomics. They bri...' WHERE id = 600 AND (agent_ids_notes IS NULL OR agent_ids_notes = '');
